{!<p class="dnvp">!}[? if flavour_2_trigger == 1 and flavour_2_trigger_time == time: Westarp and his group of <span style="color: #3E88B3;">**DNVP**</span> moderates have been finding their new home in the newly founded <span style="color: #0087DC;">Conservative People's Party</span> (<span style="color: #0087DC;">**KVP**</span>), <span style="color: #7FCEB1;">**CNBLP**</span>[? if stegerwald_path == 0:&nbsp;and <span style="color: #8ED8E4;">**CSVD**</span>?], who are to contest the next election. ?]{!</p>!}

