{!<p class="other">!}[? if year = 1930 and month = 11 : The <span style="color: #C8102E;">Austrian Social Democrats</span> have won the recent legislative election, securing a majority of seats in their *Nationalrat*. However a right-wing coalition of the <span style="color: #000000;">Christian Social Party</span> and minor bourgeois parties once again has excluded them from government. The Austrian branch of the <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**NSDAP**</span> have received 3% of the vote, and the political wing of the <span style="color: #ABDDA4;">Heimwehr</span> (comparable to our *Freikorps*) garnered 6%. This is particularly concerning, as the <span style="color: #C8102E;">Austrian Social Democrats</span> lost votes despite the economic depression occurring while they were in opposition, suggesting the electorate is looking for answers on the right. ?]{!</p>!}

